\subtree{
\title{Success Criteria}
\ul{
\li{[ ] Output directory resolved (user-specified or auto-incremented default)}
\li{[ ] All generated files stored inside \code{\startverb $OUTPUT_DIR\stopverb}}
\li{[ ] Languages detected with file counts; Pro status checked}
\li{[ ] Scan mode selected by user (run all / important only)}
\li{[ ] Rulesets include third-party rules for all detected languages}
\li{[ ] User explicitly approved the scan plan (Step 3 gate passed)}
\li{[ ] All scan Tasks spawned in a single message and completed}
\li{[ ] Every \code{\startverb semgrep\stopverb} command used \code{\startverb --metrics=off\stopverb}}
\li{[ ] Approved rulesets logged to \code{\startverb $OUTPUT_DIR/rulesets.txt\stopverb}}
\li{[ ] Raw per-scan outputs stored in \code{\startverb $OUTPUT_DIR/raw/\stopverb}}
\li{[ ] \code{\startverb results.sarif\stopverb} exists in \code{\startverb $OUTPUT_DIR/results/\stopverb} and is valid JSON}
\li{[ ] Important-only mode: post-filter applied before merge; unfiltered results preserved in \code{\startverb raw/\stopverb}}
\li{[ ] Results summary reported with severity and category breakdown}
\li{[ ] Cloned repos (if any) cleaned up from \code{\startverb $OUTPUT_DIR/repos/\stopverb}}
}
}
}